com.facebook.litho

Interface DiffNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultDiffNode

    public interface DiffNode
extends java.lang.Cloneable
    A lightweight representation of a layout node, used to cache measurements between two Layout tree calculations.
